ed Sprites for Performance Improvements</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed headline loader bug when 1 column was selected and a post has a single comment</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed overflow bug for some mobile devices for 300px sidebar</li>\r\n				<li>Added missing translation string in review posts</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nheader.php\r\nstyle.css\r\nstyle.php\r\ncustom.js.php\r\nreview.php\r\ndefault.po\r\ndefault.mo\r\n\r\n============\r\nAdded Files\r\n============\r\nsprites.png\r\n\r\n============\r\nRemoved Files\r\n============\r\nscroll-top.png\r\nnavarrows-dark.png\r\nnavarrows-top.png\r\nbullets.png\r\narrows.png\r\nunnecessary external javascript files\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.3.2</strong> October 16, 2012</h4>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>Fixed Bug Date in Top Bar</li>\r\n				<li>Updated Isotope Plugin to Isotope v1.5.20 for FireFox 16 compatibility</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nheader.php\r\nstyle.css\r\ncustom.js.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.3.1</strong> October 15, 2012</h4>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>Fixed warning message when related posts have no tags.</li>\r\n				<li>Randomized related posts.</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nstyle.css\r\nextra-functions.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.3</strong> October 13, 2012</h4>\r\n			<strong>New Features</strong>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>Added Author Pages</li>\r\n				<li>Added a Boxed Layout Option</li>\r\n				<li>Easier Background Color Option</li>\r\n				<li>Added optional content area to homepage templates</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>Fixed issues with addtional styling of fonts</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed date localization issue</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nsheader.php\r\noptions.php\r\nsingle.php\r\nstyle.css\r\ntemplate-home-slider.php\r\ntemplate-home.php\r\nextra-functions.php\r\nonecol.php\r\ntwocol.php\r\nstyle.php\r\nwidget-news.php\r\ndefault.po\r\ndefault.mo\r\n\r\n==========\r\nAdded  Files\r\n==========\r\nauthor.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n		<h4><strong>Hotfix – Version 1.2.1</strong> October 11, 2012</h4>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Fixed deprecated twitter function as of Oct 11, 2012.</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nwidget-twitter.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n				<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.2</strong> October 8, 2012</h4>\r\n				<strong>New Features</strong>\r\n				<ol>\r\n					<li>Added 300px sidebar layout option for increased ad support</li>\r\n					<li>Added integrated related posts functionality to single pages</li>	\r\n				</ol>\r\n				<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>\r\n				<ol>\r\n					<li>Fixed "popular posts" translation issue</li>\r\n				</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nheader.php\r\nindex.php\r\noptions.php\r\nsingle.php\r\nstyle.css\r\nie7.css\r\nstyle.php\r\nextra-functions.php\r\ntwocol.php\r\ncustom.js.php\r\ndefault.po\r\ndefault.mo\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Hotfix – Version 1.1.1</strong> October 5, 2012</h4>\r\n			<strong>New Features</strong>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Added comments anchor tag to direct to comments part of post</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Fixed bug in tags page when tag has more than one word</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\nhcomments.php\r\nstyle.css\r\ntag.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.1</strong> October 3, 2012</h4>\r\n			<strong>New Features</strong>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>One Column Layout Options on Blog Index Pages and Homepage Non-Featured Posts</li>\r\n				<li>Added Schema Microdata for Review Posts</li>	\r\n				<li>Images and videos in content area are now automatically responsive.</li>\r\n				<li>Eliminated excess http requests for javascript calls - all theme jquery is now in 1 file.\r\n				</li>	\r\n			</ol>\r\n			<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Column Shortcodes now only show in single posts and pages</li>\r\n				<li>*An additional thumbnail size was added, so you''ll need to regenerate thumbnails when updating.</li>	\r\n			</ul>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\ncategory.php\r\nfunctions.php\r\nindex.php\r\noptions.php\r\nsingle.php\r\nstyle.css\r\ntag.php\r\ntemplate-home-slider.php\r\ntemplate-home.php\r\nextra-functions.php\r\nreview.php\r\ncustom.js.php\r\ndocumentation.pdf\r\n\r\n=========\r\nAdded Files\r\n=========\r\nonecol.php\r\ntwocol.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n			<h4><strong>Update – Version 1.01</strong> October 1, 2012</h4>\r\n			<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>Fixed bug in search</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed Safari Z-index Issue</li>	\r\n				<li>Minor update to heading structure</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed documentation typos</li>\r\n				<li>Fixed Text widget width in upper area</li>	\r\n				<li>Added additional padding to gallery in mobile sizes</li>\r\n				<li>Changed ajax category dropdown to parent categories only.</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n<div class="ag-pre-container">\r\n<pre class="ag-pre">\r\n============\r\nChanged Files\r\n============\r\ncategory.php\r\npage.php\r\nsingle.php\r\nstyle.css\r\ntag.php\r\nstyle.php\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n		]]>\r\n	</changelog>\r\n</notifier>', 'yes'),
